 1998-03151998-03-100,  ,  ,  ,  HERITAGE
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of JANE DRAGON, of Fort Smith, Northwest Territories, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Joe Wai, whose term has expired.

precis:
